---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="My Games">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-4">
  
    <!-- Spy Within Us -->
    <div>
      <strong class="block text-white text-xl font-bold">Spy Within Us</strong>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        is a live multiplayer social‑deduction game where one hidden Imposter crafts AI‑driven prompts alongside collaborators—and you must vote them out before they prevail.
      </p>
      <a href="/spy" class="block mt-2">
        <button
          class="w-full border-2 border-red-500 border-b-[3px] text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-red-600 hover:text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-medium"
        >
          🔮 Play Spy Within Us
        </button>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="h-1"></div>
  
    <!-- Prompt Quest -->
    <div>
      <strong class="block text-white text-xl font-bold">Prompt Quest</strong>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        is a multiplayer AI‑powered storytelling game that sparks imagination through playful, constraint‑driven challenges.
      </p>
      <a href="/prompt-quest" class="block mt-2">
        <button
          class="w-full border-2 border-red-500 border-b-[3px] text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-red-600 hover:text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-medium"
        >
          🧩 Play Prompt Quest
        </button>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        Beyond my work in AI, gaming has always been a personal passion representing India at the 2018 Asian Games.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Card>
